    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to Gradation 1 per MRL 2 requirements for Class II CPB devices with Medium model influence. Discretization error exceeds requirements at Gradation 3. Validation results confirm CFD model predicts hemolysis index within 15% of experimental measurements across all 5 operating points. RH < 1.0 acceptance criterion satisfied. The assessment methodology follows the approach described in the hemolysis CFD literature (Morrison et al., J. Biomech. Eng. 2022) and the model is credible for the stated COU.",
